---
title: Sweet Soy Chicken & Ponzu Slaw with Sesame Kumara Fries & Mayo
description: This chicken has layers upon layers of flavour, first being cooked in our staple sweet-soy seasoning, then being tossed in sweet
chilli! Sesame-crusted kūmara fries and a crunchy, zingy slaw act as the perfect side-kicks to this superstar dish.
